    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid), over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced chestnut mushrooms</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until they're starting to brown</p>",
